{"tid":1448861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【巨額補償】一個係毀容致盲女抗爭者、另一個係警察","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:36:05.000Z","uid":120404,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58399e0fab044eee2ed6484814b975df309c0bd9","tid":1448861,"uid":120404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"毀容致盲女抗爭者唔洗多解釋<br />\n而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">巨額補償</span></strong>另一個點解會係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警察</strong></span>？<br />\n而且有機會將整場運動<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">翻盤</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要該名警察（或多於一名）<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>提供證據</strong></span><br />\n而該批證據於法庭上<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>直接導致副處長或以上負上刑責</strong></span><br />\n即可得到巨額補償<br />\n補償其警員職位損失及所承受壓力<br />\n<br />\n若有警察有種企出尼<br />\n其實等同自殺<br />\n唔可能要佢白白送頭<br />\n<br />\n只要金額夠大<br />\n成不成功都可以分化整個警隊<br />\n成功更可重擊警隊以至政府<br />\n----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n幾十歲人今晚真係有眼淚<br />\n希望可以為各軍師帶來啟發"},{"pid":"1d7d4e376be8bde2d97273ff4a9dcc6ee9b27a7f","tid":1448861,"uid":120404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d325e3e7249f15ab37c19b72bba8db901f504a46","tid":1448861,"uid":41290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56788499a945e8cdf2e78c362636f82e30ccfdfe","tid":1448861,"uid":261885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93b4a1018d2e21a635cced3ef1627f52c90826ac","tid":1448861,"uid":4298,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:59.000Z","msg":"呢個方法都唔錯 <br />\n但要確保佢真係有用自保償<br />\n我第一個支持<br />\n<br />\nPS 個女仔我一世助養都得"},{"pid":"e09fa6b5cebdb01cbe35420857f04f64562d26a9","tid":1448861,"uid":271413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"做得狗仲有良知？唔好唔記得律政司都係佢地人"},{"pid":"72695ca723946ac6cfe6fd0825c1d4c3453b3bf6","tid":14